                        p.home__opiniones__text Come and learn everything about Argentina through a 6 wines-flight (at least!). Book your glass!
                        a(href="#").home__opiniones__button Check here
                    .home__opiniones__column
                        .home__opiniones__column-image
                            img(src="/images/home/illustration-special-tasting.png")
                        h3.home__opiniones__column-title Special Tastings
                        p.home__opiniones__column-subtitle They can happen any time!
                        p.home__opiniones__text We love to make tastings, different topics, regions, wineries, style of wines... and those we most love: ICONS tastings (yes, what you are imaging).
                        a(href="#").home__opiniones__button Check here
                    .home__opiniones__column
                        .home__opiniones__column-image
